metadata.name: Exquisite
metadata.description:
"Exquisite" by Cafe_Flor, an award-winning artist with a background in floral design who ventured into NFT creation in 2021, embodies the captivating fusion of elegance and Surrealism.

This AI-generated artwork pays homage to the esteemed Exquisite Workers project and their three-year daily exploration of digital "exquisite corpses."Â 

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibit at Oculus NYC, hosted by Exquisite Workers and Superchief Gallery NFT, June 2-8, 2023, curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
